    <h2 id="workflows">
      Workflows:
    </h2>

    <h3 id="systemlessbrgreater">
      System<br>
    </h3>

  <p>
    The main challenge here was to build a cohesive experience around an existing platform, while supporting very low latency Video streaming in an extremely noisy RF environment.<br>    This involved reverse-engineering the RC tanks' electrical layout and signalling structure, then finding creative ways to interpret the internal system state without interrupting it's operation.
  </p>

  <p>
    
  </p>

    <figure class="post__image post__image--center">
      <img loading="lazy" src="https://parthmbhatt.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/1/system-overview.png" height="720" width="1280" alt=""  sizes="(min-width: 37.5em) 1600px, 80vw" srcset="https://parthmbhatt.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/1/responsive/system-overview-xs.png 384w ,https://parthmbhatt.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/1/responsive/system-overview-sm.png 600w ,https://parthmbhatt.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/1/responsive/system-overview-md.png 768w ,https://parthmbhatt.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/1/responsive/system-overview-lg.png 1200w ,https://parthmbhatt.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/1/responsive/system-overview-xl.png 1600w">
      <figcaption>Simplified system structure</figcaption>
